  "Factory Rework Pairing : HFM or CID": {
   "width": 13980,
   "height": 12300,
   "color": "rgb(0,0,255)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "FACTORY REWORK : HFM or Customer ID pairing  ",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 120,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 13560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "PROCEDURE",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 2520,
      "height": 1605,
      "width": 13560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Insert the \"After Sales code\" (16 bytes), complete the additionnal pairing data (optional), select \"StartRoutine\" and press \"ENTER REWORK MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 3120,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 13080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) If the REWORK MODE for HFM pairing is launched, then approach a CID belonging to the vehicle to the Kazashi ring or transponder antenna",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 4800,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 6360
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) Once all the customer IDs are paired, validate and press the button \"EXIT REWORK MODE\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6600,
      "top": 7440,
      "height": 960,
      "width": 7080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID / HFM INFORMATION",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6600,
      "top": 9480,
      "height": 2640,
      "width": 7080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Select \"StartRoutine\" and press the button \"CID ANALYSE\"",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 600,
      "height": 1800,
      "width": 8280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "PAIRING INFORMATION",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 8520,
      "height": 840,
      "width": 13560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "REWORK MODE FAILURES",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 9480,
      "height": 2640,
      "width": 6360
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) Select\"StartRoutine\" and press \"CID Pairing\" to pair a customer ID",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6600,
      "top": 5520,
      "height": 1800,
      "width": 7080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) Enter REWORK MODE again to launch the customer ID pairing, then approach a CID belonging to the vehicle, or blank, to the Kazashi ring or transponder antenna",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6600,
      "top": 4800,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 7080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Select \"StartRoutine\" and press \"HFM pairing\" to pair the HFM",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 5520,
      "height": 1800,
      "width": 6360
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) If the HFM is paired, the EXIT of the REWORK MODE is automatic. Then pair all the customers IDs (procedure in right)",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 7440,
      "height": 960,
      "width": 6360
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "After Sales Code",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 3600,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 1815
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "HFM Rework Mode",
     "color": "rgb(0,0,255)",
     "alignment": "1",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1200,
      "top": 4320,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 2115
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID Rework Mode",
     "color": "rgb(0,0,255)",
     "alignment": "1",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 8520,
      "top": 4320,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 1920
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 11.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "return code status",
     "color": "rgb(223,223,223)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 3960,
