  "Aftersales Pairing : HFM": {
   "width": 13860,
   "height": 11460,
   "color": "rgb(128,0,128)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Protected Pairing : HFM pairing in After Sales ",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,128)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 0,
      "height": 315,
      "width": 13560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "PROCEDURE",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 2520,
      "height": 5880,
      "width": 13560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) /!\\ Check Ignition is OFF and  that you have access rights to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\" on https://gco.intra.renault.fr:14053/gco/ctrl/login",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 3240,
      "height": 525,
      "width": 13080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Press \"Request Server HFM pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 3840,
      "height": 255,
      "width": 9600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Select \"Input_Data_To_Server\" (19 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 4920,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 9480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Get the \"Server answer\" (16 bytes) and copy it in this screen. Then press \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 5520,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 10680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) If the HFM is SA unlocked for HFM pairing then: approach the card belonging to the vehicle to the pairing antenna and press \"HFM Pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 6960,
      "height": 555,
      "width": 13080
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID / HFM INFORMATION",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 7095,
      "top": 8640,
      "height": 2640,
      "width": 6585
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA FAILURE",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 8640,
      "height": 2640,
      "width": 6840
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Pairing procedure exit is automatic. If the HFM is not SA unlocked , press ABORT",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,255,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 8040,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 7590
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "HFM Pairing SA Unlocked",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,128)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 720,
      "top": 6480,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 2535
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6713 +",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 3840,
      "top": 4320,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 720
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "(17 bytes)",
     "color": "rgb(128,128,255)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 9360,
      "top": 4320,
