  "Aftersales Pairing : CID": {
   "width": 13860,
   "height": 13980,
   "color": "rgb(0,64,128)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Protected Pairing : Customer ID pairing in After Sales ",
     "color": "rgb(39,198,216)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 0,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 13560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "PROCEDURE",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 2520,
      "height": 7560,
      "width": 13560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) Approach the customer ID to the Kazashi ring and press the button \"CID Analyse\" to check its presence and status",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 3600,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 12720
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Complete PAIRING_PARAMETER (8 bytes, IDE1 and IDE2) and press \"Request Server CID pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 4080,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Select the \"Input Data Server\" (19 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\" ",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 5160,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 8760
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Get the \"Server Answer\" (16 bytes) from \"Pairing DDT2000\" and press \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 6120,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11880
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) If the BCM is SA unlocked for CID pairing, approach a blank CID to the Kazashi and press the button \"CID pairing\"  ",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 7680,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 10920
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) Repeat Step 5 for all CIDs to pair",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 8640,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 6840
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID / BCM INFORMATION",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6960,
      "top": 10200,
      "height": 2520,
      "width": 6720
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "PAIRING INFORMATION",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 3120,
      "top": 12840,
      "height": 840,
      "width": 7560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA FAILURES ",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 10200,
      "height": 2520,
      "width": 6720
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) If all CIDs are paired, type \"01 and \"press \"Exit procedure\"",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 9120,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 8640
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "!! Check that you have access rights to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\"",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 3120,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 9360
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CID SA unlocked",
     "color": "rgb(179,230,240)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 480,
      "top": 7080,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 1680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Select \"StartRoutine\" and press the button \"CID ANALYSE\"",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 600,
      "height": 1800,
      "width": 8280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 9.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "::pic:electric\\high_voltage_64x64",
     "color": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 7680,
      "top": 720,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
