  "Aftersales Pairing : ECM": {
   "width": 13260,
   "height": 12300,
   "color": "rgb(128,0,0)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Engine Control Module: After Sales Protected Pairing",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(15,15,15)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 0,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 12960
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "PROCEDURE",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 480,
      "height": 8160,
      "width": 12960
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Check that the ECM is blank (try to start the vehicle) and read the ECM information \" ECM_IS_BLANK\"",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 1680,
      "height": 285,
      "width": 8775
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Press the button \"Request Server ECM pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 2280,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 8790
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Select the \"Input_Data_to_server\" (19 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 3240,
      "height": 255,
      "width": 8775
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) Complete the frames in the application and press the button \"Calcul\". Get the \"Server answer\" (16 bytes) and copy it in SERVER_ANSWER. Then press the button \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 4200,
      "height": 615,
      "width": 12240
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) !! Check that you have access rights to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\" on https://gco.intra.renault.fr:14053/gco/ctrl/login",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 1080,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 11640
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6) If the HFM is SA unlocked for ECM pairing then put the Ignition Power Supply OFF, select \"startRoutine\" and press the button \"Authorize ECM pairing\" ",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 5880,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 12600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "7) If the authorization to pair is TRUE, then switch Ignition Power Supply ON. If the ECM is paired, procedure exit is automatic.",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 7560,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 12240
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "ECM / HFM INFORMATION",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 7080,
      "top": 8760,
      "height": 3360,
      "width": 6000
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA FAILURE",
     "color": "rgb(0,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 8760,
      "height": 2640,
      "width": 6840
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "MS Sans Serif",
      "size": 8.25,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "8) To postpone the authorization to pair the ECM, press the button",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 360,
      "top": 8160,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 6600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "SA Unlocked for ECM pairing",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 840,
      "top": 5400,
      "height": 315,
      "width": 3495
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Authorization to pair ECM",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 7080,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 3495
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "6717 +",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1200,
      "top": 3720,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 720
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "(17 bytes)",
     "color": "rgb(207,207,207)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 6600,
      "top": 3720,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 1200
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "1"
     }
    }
   ],
